<br>
Currently it is one of the harder, longer (on the scale of several months compared to weeks or days for many other more powerful epics *coughclericcough*) yet warriors get ridiculed if they use their epic! So it is about time that either the quest to be changed to fit the reward or for the reward to be changed to fit the difficulty of the quest.<br>
